{"title":"三访海南","authors":["关山月"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三访海南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游鼓岭遇雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文昌多胜境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后鼓山游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车走披荆路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔图东咀沟；①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛奔万马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽石顶千牛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷电声光急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风驰返龙楼。②"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万宁赴三亚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨起攀登东山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午休再赶鹿回头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪看车外猎奇景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉我胶林绿海游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重访鹿回头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年阔别鹿回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再度天涯海角游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鹭飞鸥曾结识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫讥画叟鬓杪秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖峰岭山麓晨起拾稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖峰岭麓出泉清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鸟啁啾伴涧鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村女溪边欢濯曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学童窗下朗书声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热林郁郁碧如海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水潺潺洁似冰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处秋光添画意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更撩墨客苦吟情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过自治州口占"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通什变天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风情不一般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郊东太平瀑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城里南圣江；③"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍岸喧宵市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿河入画廊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮光掠影过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造化师无方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华侨农场胶林赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行程最后抵兴隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再醉橡胶林海中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画叟贪游意未足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯看绿浪接晴空。注：①渔港名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②原公社所在地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"③江河名"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}